data.description: One story, hard-to-find 4/3/2 on the East side, near the High School in Jacksonville. Four year old metal roof,  2277 SF, with gas cooktop and oven, hardwood floors in living area and wood-burning fireplace.  Kitchen with breakfast bar.  Huge split master bedroom with French doors leading to backyard pergola.  Nice sized fenced backyard and workshop with electric and built in shelving and drawers as well as area for storage.  By appointment only.  Call today before your chance at this 4 bedroom home is gone!
